{"tid":390613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳克儉促家長加把勁關心學生","createTime":"2017-09-07T07:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T08:32:00.000Z","uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fafb265524470fb762edfd61b5440413ca0e6fc","tid":390613,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1383992/再有學生輕生%20%20吳克儉促老師家長加把勁關心\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1383992%2F%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%BC%95%E7%94%9F%2520%2520%E5%90%B3%E5%85%8B%E5%84%89%E4%BF%83%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%8A%A0%E6%8A%8A%E5%8B%81%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83&d=tkmTD006pdmnVmn%2Fno3as54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=70322ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1383992/再有學生輕生%20%20吳克儉促老師家長加把勁關心</a><br />\n<br />\n再有學生輕生 吳克儉促老師家長加把勁關心<br />\n 18:10 2016/03/06 <br />\n開學至今已累計有15名學生自殺輕生，包括昨日一名中大醫科學生，教育局局長吳克儉今日被問及局方有什麼跟進工作時，他只表示「上星期立法會已回應相關提問」，又促同學們要有堅毅精神，學校、老師及家長要加把勁，多關心、多輔助，讓同學了解「辦法比問題多」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然吳克儉對再有學生輕生感痛心及關注，但被問及局方會否建議大學設精神科、加強心理輔導時，吳克儉只重申，大學教育資助委員會向8間院校提供的資助，院校可自主處理。"},{"pid":"ddf541735eeb59b362d5a46b75cd7cf3b89306a3","tid":390613,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:07:06.000Z","msg":"副局長今晚收工跳埋落去關心佢個仔啦👍🏿👍🏿😂😂"},{"pid":"1a5a035c26a7666ddaad53936844efe428a1efa4","tid":390613,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lh6.ggpht.com/-0ZJiz606Ljs/UptXF9KDCFI/AAAAAAAAA58/977Kk5617_w/s0/meow.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh6.ggpht.com%2F-0ZJiz606Ljs%2FUptXF9KDCFI%2FAAAAAAAAA58%2F977Kk5617_w%2Fs0%2Fmeow.gif&h=62eb56b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬隊友系列"},{"pid":"318612aba38ba7bcfe8e8c35e5d3197ad68a93b5","tid":390613,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/